quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"Rabbana amanna bimaanzalta wattabaAAna arrasoola faktubnamaAAa ashshahideen"
  3,54,"Wamakaroo wamakara Allahu wallahukhayru almakireen"
  3,55,"Ith qala Allahu yaAAeesa innee mutawaffeeka warafiAAuka ilayya wamutahhirukamina allatheena kafaroo wajaAAilu allatheenaittabaAAooka fawqa allatheena kafaroo ila yawmialqiyamati thumma ilayya marjiAAukum faahkumubaynakum feema kuntum feehi takhtalifoon"
  3,56,"Faamma allatheena kafaroofaoAAaththibuhum AAathaban shadeedan fee addunyawal-akhirati wama lahum min nasireen"
  3,57,"Waamma allatheena amanoowaAAamiloo assalihati fayuwaffeehimojoorahum wallahu la yuhibbu aththalimeen"
  3,58,"Thalika natloohu AAalayka mina al-ayatiwaththikri alhakeem"
  3,59,"Inna mathala AAeesa AAinda Allahikamathali adama khalaqahu min turabin thumma qalalahu kun fayakoon"
  3,60,"Alhaqqu min rabbika fala takunmina almumtareen"
  3,61,"Faman hajjaka feehi min baAAdi majaaka mina alAAilmi faqul taAAalaw nadAAu abnaanawaabnaakum wanisaana wanisaakumwaanfusana waanfusakum thumma nabtahil fanajAAal laAAnataAllahi AAala alkathibeen"
